{"tid":984689,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南京房地產老闆負債二億上吊身亡    分析估計明年有九成中小房企退市","createTime":"2019-01-17T04:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T13:45:24.000Z","uid":141151,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b9e64ab5b50790259592a7e52262ebf599c96f36","tid":984689,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:02:03.000Z","msg":"【南京房地產老闆負債二億上吊身亡】<br />\n【分析估計明年有九成中小房企退市】<br />\n<br />\n「房子不是用來炒的。」習近平講了這句近三年。<br />\n<br />\n不少發展商近年都面對融資困難，有地產商老闆懷疑因負債纍纍結束生命。曾被媒體選為南京房地產市場十大推動人之一的張旭東被證實在1月7日上吊身亡。<br />\n<br />\n有消息人士指，「原來的幾個股東，一次性四個股東全部撤走，政府給他原來答應的300畝地，當地有協議，現在300畝地不給他了，導致張旭東崩潰了。」<br />\n<br />\n安徽白鷺島是張旭東最重視的項目，四萬多畝的度假村投資額超過四億元，但度假村都未完全落成，張旭東就因為欠下近兩億元債務，被迫以一元的價錢將股份轉讓。<br />\n<br />\n張旭東自殺的消息傳出後，有分析認為是揭示了中央收緊房地產資金下，中小型發展商的經營困境。有內地媒體統計，單在去年已有十多間發展商因資金鏈斷裂而破產，但同一時間，龍頭發展商的身家就水漲船高。中國指數研究院公布去年有156間發展商銷售額突破百億元，比前年多12間。<br />\n<br />\n新城控股高級副總裁歐陽捷分析，發展商規模競賽愈演愈烈，估計到明年，將會有九成中小企退出市場，而20間龍頭發展商將會佔據六成以上的市場。<br />\n<br />\n#樓市泡沬<br />\n#房地產市場<br />\n#房地產發展商<br />\n#房子不是用來抄的<br />\n#有線中國組"},{"pid":"9736421a80f6ed2a6f9ead34fe662a768f39a625","tid":984689,"uid":26752,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:03:48.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>被迫以一元的價錢將股份轉讓</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div><br />\n<br />\n抄家"},{"pid":"a9928f35d8a2e932920165a56d78d0eb5a3f947f","tid":984689,"uid":20241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:19:22.000Z","msg":"有咁耐風流"},{"pid":"b7a63adc84dbc047f6c56fb09bfc5025982c42da","tid":984689,"uid":10056,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:40:13.000Z","msg":"最後都係益哂d大發展商真係仆街黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45fdadaec46130d4847de00c1f7fca91aa7be2ce","tid":984689,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T11:46:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf277bb2129d4eb4b04623657a2458da5056628","tid":984689,"uid":166766,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b7a63adc84dbc047f6c56fb09bfc5025982c42da","tid":984689,"uid":10056,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:40:13.000Z","msg":"最後都係益哂d大發展商真係仆街黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T12:01:34.000Z","msg":"以前水浸就會群魔亂舞   靠關係  咩人都可以做地產<br />\n當經濟一有問題  銀行唔借錢   <br />\n自然就得返市場龍頭生存到    好多暴利行業都係咁<br />\n不如語條友唔識退  冇後台"},{"pid":"9d76c9a0ffe54ecb0745a75ca002286a78dc22bc","tid":984689,"uid":57376,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:25:24.000Z","msg":"咪即係國進民退<br />\n之前仲話唔會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4176d6713800c53bd176eadadaee139a4c8a9b07","tid":984689,"uid":107023,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:26:51.000Z","msg":"變相強迫性共你產姐<br />\n收緊資金，迫你賤價賣股權，大食細食到得番有後台的大野"},{"pid":"aee4b473087d11c0c486a48d07c46865caee3bd2","tid":984689,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618ba51e13535bc47813912293a4f42b3dffc674","tid":984689,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:45:00.000Z","msg":"一起共產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一起發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/